metadata.name: Golestan
metadata.description:
Golestan means Garden of Roses in Persian. This photo was taken in Golestan Palace at Tehran in 2018. Golestan Palace is one of the oldest monuments in the city of Tehran and it is in World Heritage List of UNESCO. Every year many people are visiting this palace. Sometimes people are praying in the tomb section of this place. This photo was taken while a young lady was praying during her visit.
